# CODEOWNERS — 默认审阅者。GitHub 据此在 PR 自动请求 review。
# 文件规则语法同 .gitignore：每行 <glob> <@user/@team>...
# 详见: https://docs.github.com/repositories/managing-your-repositories-settings-and-features/customizing-your-repository/about-code-owners
#
# ⚠️ 请将下方占位 @your-handle 改为实际 GitHub 用户名/团队。

# 默认：仓库内所有文件
*                           @your-handle

# 示例：按目录细分
# /src/core/                @your-handle @core-reviewer
# /docs/                    @docs-team
# /.github/                 @your-handle
# /Cargo.toml /Cargo.lock   @your-handle
